messageBody:
Erik (with a k, not liza with a z)...

Yo baby. You so good to me.

But!

I hereby bite on your trollbait. What the hell is an rss feed and why
do I want one?

Hill

P.S. I'm embarrassed to report that I am practically living in
Oakland, and I didn't call you. I stand before you--no wait--I sit
before you, consumed with guilt. I'll be back the first working week
of January. Perhaps we should, ummmm, consult, face-to-face?
